{"word":"ῥώξ 1","slug":"ῥώξ 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92931\" key=\"r(w/c1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥώξ</orth> (A), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥωγός, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ῥήγνυμι</etym>) <sense id=\"n92931.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">breach</tr_>: in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:143\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.143</biblScope></bibl>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνὰ ῥῶγας μεγάροιο</foreign>, the sense is dub.; it seems to mean <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">narrow entrances</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">passages leading to</tr_> the hall.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}